    "This way, we identified 497 SVs that initially were not identified in Illumina but were genotyped as present.",
    "We identified 484 non-germline SVs using Sniffles2 that have Illumina read support in the neighboring brain region, thus showing that Snif-fles2 is able to accurately detect low-frequency (that is, mosaic) SVs.",
    "Given these advancements in mosaic and germline calling, we further tested Sniffles2 across COLO829/COLO829BL.",
    "Figure 5d shows the overlap across ONT and PacBio calling using Sniffles.",
    "Details on the results are in Supplementary Section 5."
